data.description: Enter your new home from the inviting covered front porch to the comfortable living room.  The separate dining room with hardwood flooring and arched doorway adds an elegant touch to the interior and is perfect for hosting dinner parties or enjoying family holidays. Eat in kitchen with gas range provides a more casual place to enjoy meals. You also have the convenience of the main floor laundry room and enclosed porch for additional space. The second floor offers two sizable bedrooms and spacious full bath.   At the rear of the home, there is a covered patio and fenced yard, providing privacy and security. Ideal  space for kids and pets  to play, gardening, outdoor gatherings, grilling, or simply hanging out. Overall, this semi-detached home combines classic design elements with practical features that make it a  welcoming place to live.  Come on out and see for yourself and make it your own!
